checklist for the theme

- register post formats for link, post, image and video
- customize post loop to show different content for different post types
- customize post grid to show titles, descriptions and post images
- ajax content loading for the posts and the projects
- templates for ajax content, should just be the_content in a box
- content template for the page sections - keep it simple
- setup plugins 
- footer image uploader in the theme options
- select which pages go in the different content blocks in the theme options
- Select post category for the news feed in the theme options
